NOTES FOR THE GIT REPOSITORY
============================

Anonymous commit to the online repository is possible to the "mob" branch.

Instructions:
------------

* Clone the repository:

git clone git+ssh://mob@repo.or.cz/srv/git/gimp-lqr-plugin.git

* Enter into the directory and get the "mob" branch:

cd gimp-lqr-plugin
git checkout -b mob
git pull origin mob

* Make your changes & commit
* Finally, upload the changes:

git push origin mob

